data.description: Great Pride of Ownership. Well-maintained grounds & exterior are superb greeting to the pristine interior. Refreshing dcor, a pleasure in every way. A comfortable lifestyle full of livability & many ways how you enjoy. Low maintenance exterior design on large .44 acre lot, room to enjoy life and space in-between neighbors. Open living areas & volume ceilings. Chef's delight's kitchen w/ lots of cabinetry, counters with tile backsplash, serving or drop off bar, SS appliances, pantry & breakfast area. Large deck for outdoor fun and relaxation. Upstairs is the serene spacious primary suite w/tranquil bath, garden tub, shower, vanity w/double bowl & walk-in closet space. 3 comfortable beds up w/access to full bath including a handy laundry room. Located in Oxford Place in Southwest Aiken County. No city taxes. Minutes to shopping, restaurants, recreational, major employers, N. Augusta and Georgia.  Live the Good Life at this sought-after home. #thesearchisover
